data.description: Motivated seller. Featuring a sprawling open floor plan with main level owners suite and 25' ceilings (complete with transom lighting!) this spacious 1.5 story home in Dakota Crossing borders devoted open space on one side and offers room for everyone to spread out- multiple living areas, eat in kitchen, private dining, and generous bedrooms, as well as a walk out basement on a private fenced lot.  Main level owners suite is complete with five piece bath, walk in closet, and a well thought out plan that allows ample natural light.  Upstairs, find a homework nook or bonus loft area, as well as three bedrooms and a bathroom with enough counter space there won't be fighting; each bedroom offers a generous closet and spacious square footage.  In the basement, a large family room, game room, two more bedrooms, a 4th bath, and storage space complete this fully finished home.
